  "title": "Operation Coordinator | Bedok | Up to $3000+Bonus | 9755",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Operation Officer</strong></p><p><strong>Industry: Environmental Services</strong></p><p><strong>Location: 2 bus stop from Bedok Mrt</strong></p><p><strong>5.5 Days | Mon to Fri 8am - 5pm | Saturday 8am - 12pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2500 - $3000 + Bonus</strong></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li>Knowledge of Horticultural or equivalent an advantage</li><li> At least 2 years in scheduling and operations management [ manpower management and logistics arrangement ]</li></ol><p></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Work closely with the operations team to manage manpower deployment across clusters islandwide.</li><li>Plan and schedule daily jobs using the company’s system to ensure timely and efficient execution.</li><li>Lead, motivate, and train team members, fostering professionalism and strong work ethics.</li><li>Troubleshoot operational challenges and step in when manpower shortages occur.</li><li>Manage and resolve disciplinary, safety, and operational issues.</li><li>Participate in recruitment and onboarding of operations team members.</li><li>Supervise operations to ensure compliance with company procedures and SOPs.</li><li>Leverage strong knowledge of Singapore roads to optimize logistics and job assignments.</li><li>Willing to work overtime (OT) when required.</li><li>Share a genuine passion for plants and contribute positively to the company’s horticultural mission.</li></ul><p><br />Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p><p></p>",
